<p>&amp; not being able to shoot back.<br/>In Lone Pine" the Turks threw a note over to our chaps saying; come out you silly - &amp; fire away we know you are there" but for all that they were not to sure for they attacked the British at Cape Helles" &amp; suffered a severe set back they caught nearly a division with machine guns on an open piece of ground &amp; nearly annilhiated then.<br/>The same day they tried the same game on the New Zealanders, but they dished them up properly, so they done a bit of good with their silence, but the main object of course was to try them &amp; see how they would act when the time came for the evacuation little did we think it would come</p>
